# Module 1: Introduction to AI for Software Development – Facilitator Guide

## ⏱ Timing
45 minutes total
- Intro + Demo: 15 min
- Activities: 20 min
- Group Discussion: 10 min

## 👩‍🏫 Key Talking Points
- AI coding assistants and their impact
- Model agnosticism: choosing the right tool for the job
- Ethics in using AI tools for development

## 🛠 Facilitation Tips
- Pause after demos to field questions
- Encourage participants to share when they’ve used larger models to solve blockers
